        reject ISO-8601 "YYYY-MM-DDTHH:MM:SSZ" form; ISO-T → space-form
        normalization at the boundary in three sites:
        src/bl.d/42-observe-router.sh (--since arg), 41-observe-collectors.sh
        (find -newermt + touch -d fallback), 83-clean.sh (dry-run
        receipt timestamp parse).
